      { heading: "The Budget Feeder: DOGNESS Mini ($99 → Often on sale)", body: "At $99 MSRP (frequently discounted), the DOGNESS Mini gives you app-controlled scheduling, a 3.5L hopper (14-18 days for one cat), stainless steel bowl, and anti-clog design. It lacks a camera, but at this price you're getting reliable automatic feeding. If the DOGNESS is over budget, the WOPET at $89 is the alternative with larger 6L capacity." },
