      { q: "What's the first thing to upgrade from this kit?", a: "The camera. A dedicated pet camera ($40-130) gives you pan/tilt, better night vision, and pet-specific features like treat tossing or bark alerts. After that, upgrade the feeder if you want a built-in camera (Petlibro Granary, $139). The Pioneer Pet fountain at $39 is already endgame quality — no urgent need to upgrade." },
